{"TopicId":173937,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Any way to move windows out of bounds?","CreatedByName":"putnamto","CreatedById":184648,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-15T20:23:46Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"putnamto","CreatedById":184648,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-15T20:23:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u00A0 have\u00A0 a\u00A0 three\u00A0 monitor\u00A0 setup\u00A0 and\u00A0 I\u00A0 play\u00A0 in\u00A0 a\u00A0 border less\u00A0 window\u00A0 mode.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u00A0 would\u00A0 be\u00A0 really\u00A0 convenient to\u00A0 be\u00A0 able\u00A0 to\u00A0 drag\u00A0 windows(like\u00A0 mechjeb, kerbnet, etc.) Over\u00A0 to\u00A0 my\u00A0 other\u00A0 monitors\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs\u00A0 this\u00A0 possible\u00A0 in\u00A0 any\u00A0 way?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u00A0 know\u00A0 I\u0027ve\u00A0 done\u00A0 this\u00A0 accidentally\u00A0 before\u00A0 when\u00A0 I\u00A0 was\u00A0 in\u00A0 full screen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-04-15T20:25:09Z\u0022 title=\u002204/15/2018 08:25  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EApril 15, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by putnamto\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"90VG","CreatedById":187229,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-16T18:19:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBump, I\u0027d like to be able to do this also.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LoSBoL","CreatedById":174038,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-17T11:22:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou could create a custom resolution and play KSP ultra super widescreen if you have more then one monitor, that will give you plenty of room to use your sidemonitors for all types of popup menu\u0027s.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00221k0.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022235\u0